### Test Attendance System API
### This file can be used with REST Client extension in VS Code

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. Register a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "Test User"
}

### 2. Login with existing user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Check in (requires token from login/register)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/check
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "check-in"
}

### 4. Check out (requires token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/check
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "check-out"
}

### 5. Get attendance history (requires token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/attendance/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
